question: Show me the top 5 customers by loan balance

result.sql_query:
SELECT 
    C.CUSTOMER_NAME, 
    SUM(CL.CURRENT_PRINCIPAL_BALANCE) AS TOTAL_LOAN_BALANCE
FROM 
    CUSTOMER_DIMENSION C
JOIN 
    CL_DETAIL_FACT CL ON C.CUSTOMER_KEY = CL.CUSTOMER_KEY
WHERE 
    CL.CURRENT_PRINCIPAL_BALANCE > 0
GROUP BY 
    C.CUSTOMER_NAME
ORDER BY 
    TOTAL_LOAN_BALANCE DESC
LIMIT 5;
